1
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,519
Wasn't I on a mission at the border?

2
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,519
What is this?

3
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,039
I've transmigrated.

4
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,560
The original host, Ning Chen.

5
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,840
At twelve, his mother died,

6
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:21,800
and he was left on the streets.

7
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,879
His birth father, Ning Ziming,

8
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,719
concerned about his own reputation,

9
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,840
brought this illegitimate son back to Ning Manor.

10
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,800
For these eight years,

11
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,520
Ning Chen was humiliated at every turn.

12
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,319
Young Master.

13
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,639
He lived in constant fear.

14
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,840
Xiao Mei.

15
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,199
Only the fourth-rank maid Xiao Mei,

16
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,360
who served him from the start,

17
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:41,360
stayed close by his side,

18
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,759
never abandoning him.

19
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:44,919
I've transmigrated and become

20
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,240
Ning Chen, illegitimate son of Da Xuan's Minister of Rites.

21
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:57,919
Second Young Master, Third Young Master.

22
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,400
Second Young Master, Third Young Master.

23
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,240
Second Young Master, Third Young Master.

24
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,879
The Fourth Young Master just woke up.

25
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,159
Whatever the matter is,

26
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,759
perhaps it can wait until tomorrow.

27
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,560
Get lost.

28
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,240
Ning Manor only has three young masters.

29
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,439
Where did this fourth one come from?

30
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,479
Have you forgotten who your master is?

31
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,159
Third Brother.

32
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,439
Throw him out!

33
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:14,680
You can't!

34
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:15,800
Get up.

35
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:16,599
Move.

36
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:17,000
Let go of me!

37
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,400
Fourth Young Master!

38
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,000
Let go of me!

39
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,560
If you want to drive me out,

40
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,680
bring Ning Ziming here.

41
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,960
Who do you think you are?

42
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,960
You're not worthy of seeing Father.

43
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,240
After all these years,

44
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,639
has he ever cared about you?

45
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:48,719
Nobody move!

46
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,680
Ning Chen, what are you doing?

47
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,919
This bastard!

48
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:54,439
Just try touching my Second Brother.

49
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,800
You asked for it.

50
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,439
So I will.

51
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,479
I...

52
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:01,960
You shut your mouth!

53
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,520
Young Master, you must not!

54
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,000
Why the hell not?

55
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,000
Today I'm taking their lives.

56
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,840
Since my life is worthless anyway,

57
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,039
dragging him down with me

58
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,000
makes it worth it.

59
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,120
Could this serious illness

60
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,879
have completely changed his temperament?

61
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,319
Fourth Brother.

62
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:22,800
Whatever it is, let's talk it out.

63
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,519
Don't do anything rash.

64
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,000
Let's talk calmly.

65
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,519
All of you, get the hell out!

66
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,800
You bastard!

67
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,279
Since when do you give orders in Ning Manor?

68
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,399
I...

69
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,399
Hurry, go!

70
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,360
Go, go, go!

71
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,000
You just wait.

72
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,319
Hurry up!

73
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:40,759
Move, move, move!

74
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:41,439
Quick, quick, quick!

75
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,439
Xiao Mei.

76
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,600
Go get a rope.

77
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,199
Tie him up.

78
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:53,839
To hell with you!

79
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,560
You miserable cur! Young Master!

80
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,519
You just wait!

81
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:57,120
Young Master.

82
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,000
This body is far too weak.

83
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,959
That outburst just now in the heat of the moment

84
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,600
drained every bit of my strength.

85
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:03,680
What do I do now?

86
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,199
Since things have come to this,

87
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,439
I might as well blow it wide open.

88
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,680
Mother!

89
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:30,279
Mother!

90
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,879
What happened now? Help me, Mother!

91
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:32,480
Ning Chen.

92
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,839
That bastard Ning Chen has gone mad!

93
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,399
He is trying to kill your son!

94
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,120
Mother!

95
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,240
Look here.

96
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,279
And here too.

97
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:42,759
Xing'er, does it hurt?

98
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,040
It hurts.

99
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:46,079
That bastard has some nerve.

100
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:46,759
Where is he?

101
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,959
He is in the woodshed.

102
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,199
Servants!

103
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,759
Follow me to the back courtyard.

104
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,360
My son, you have worked hard.

105
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:58,959
These past few days,

106
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,319
how did the Imperial Examination go?

107
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,560
With my own abilities

108
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,600
and Father's and Grandfather's arrangements,

109
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,319
Zhuangyuan aside,

110
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:08,199
Bangyan or Tanhua, for me,

111
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:09,639
would be a breeze.

112
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,079
Excellent, excellent.

113
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,480
You must be exhausted these past days.

114
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:15,720
I shall have someone stew an old hen

115
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,800
to nourish you properly.

116
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,199
Thank you, Father.

117
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,439
Hurry, go, go!

118
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:22,800
Running around in a panic. Father,

119
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,680
where are your manners? Eldest Brother,

120
00:06:24,519 --> 00:06:24,920
Third Brother,

121
00:06:25,839 --> 00:06:26,560
what has happened?

122
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:28,120
You are finally back!

123
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,680
That bastard Ning Chen has gone mad!

124
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,839
He not only injured me

125
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,959
but also tried to kill Second Brother!

126
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,680
Nonsense.

127
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,319
Ning Chen has always been timid.

128
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,120
He dares not even speak loudly in the manor.

129
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,040
How could he commit such violence?

130
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:40,319
Father, it is absolutely true.

131
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,000
He stabbed Second Brother in the neck!

132
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,839
Blood was all over the floor!

133
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:44,639
Third Son.

134
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:47,839
Could there be some misunderstanding?

135
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,439
Where is Ning Chen now?

136
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,560
The woodshed.

137
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,000
That rebellious son.

138
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:57,120
Come, follow me to see

139
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,800
what on earth he is trying to do.

140
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:03,319
How dare you!

141
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,759
What are you doing with that tung oil?

142
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:06,319
Madam.

143
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,199
I am the Matriarch of Ning Manor,

144
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,199
and also your mother.

145
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,560
Why do you not kneel?

146
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,160
Did you not hear Mother speak?

147
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,399
Kneel down at once!

148
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,040
Young Master.

149
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,680
Mother?

150
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,800
My mother died long ago.

151
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:23,199
No.

152
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,480
Mother, he is insulting you!

153
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,160
Silence!

154
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,680
Truly raised in some wretched backwater.

155
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,199
You understand nothing.

156
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:33,240
I am the daughter of the Left Chancellor,

157
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,600
the Matriarch of Ning Manor.

158
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,319
For you to call me Mother

159
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,600
would be a blessing from your ancestors.

160
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,040
But clearly your ancestors lacked virtue.

161
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:40,920
You...

162
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,480
Guards!

163
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,800
Break his legs for me!

164
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,000
Stop right there!

165
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,439
Come at me if you wish to die.

166
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:48,879
What is going on here?

167
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:51,279
You have some nerve!

168
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,240
Bastard!

169
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,319
What mischief are you stirring up now?

170
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,480
Father!

171
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:58,160
He was trying to kill your child!

172
00:07:58,839 --> 00:07:59,399
Look at this!

173
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,319
Fourth Brother,

174
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,120
what do you think you are doing?

175
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,759
Father is here, yet still you dare be so rude?

176
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,319
Have you forgotten

177
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:09,759
all that I, your elder brother, have taught you?

178
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,199
What have you ever taught me?

179
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:14,680
And also,

180
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:17,920
how is it I do not recall

181
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,439
that I even have a father?

182
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,639
You rebellious son!

183
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,199
Do you even know what you are saying?

184
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:25,319
Two days ago, I was pushed into the lake by scoundrels.

185
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,600
And you, my so-called parents,

186
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,600
showed no concern at all.

187
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,439
Had I been treated sooner,

188
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,080
I would not have fallen so gravely ill.

189
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,879
Fourth son,

190
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,080
this matter of you falling into the lake,

191
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,679
how is it that we knew nothing of it?

192
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,279
Knew nothing?

193
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,200
Truly Mother's three precious darlings.

194
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:53,720
You cover for her like this

195
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,360
just to keep her from earning

196
00:08:56,559 --> 00:08:58,080
a name for cruelty and malice.

197
00:08:58,879 --> 00:09:01,159
Why has his temperament changed so suddenly?

198
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:06,879
Father.

199
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,080
Though he is my Fourth Brother,

200
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,279
he twists right and wrong,

201
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,399
framing you and Mother.

202
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,879
He must still be taught a lesson.

203
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:15,840
Very well, then.

204
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,440
A small punishment as a warning.

205
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,360
Thirty strokes of the cane.

206
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,279
So in your heart I'm only worth thirty strokes?

207
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,720
Why not just burn me to death?

208
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,279
Today I will return my life

209
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,600
to Minister Ning.

210
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,639
I doubt you have the nerve.

211
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,120
Too easy.

212
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,320
Father!

213
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,240
Burn him to death!

214
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,840
Burn him! Burn him!

215
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:45,200
Come on!

216
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,679
Damn.

217
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:52,799
You've got to be kidding.

218
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,039
I see now, you wretched boy.

219
00:09:59,360 --> 00:09:59,879
You're acting this crazy

220
00:09:59,879 --> 00:10:01,279
just to get my attention.

221
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:02,519
The more you do this,

222
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:03,919
the more I detest you.

223
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,279
Fine.

224
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,759
In that case,

225
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,759
today we sever our family ties.

226
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,480
From this day forward,

227
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:18,440
we are strangers on separate paths,

228
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,960
never to meet again.

229
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,159
You...

230
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:32,480
Ning Chen!

231
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,279
You wound me like this

232
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,840
and think you can just walk away?

233
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,360
If you have a problem, come at me!

234
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:37,840
I...

235
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,639
How crude.

236
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,879
As a Young Master of Ning Manor,

237
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,559
how could I stoop to your level?

238
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,799
However,

239
00:10:46,519 --> 00:10:48,360
after living in Ning Manor all these years,

240
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:49,799
now that you wish to leave,

241
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:50,720
we must at least

242
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,759
give you a thorough inspection.

243
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:57,000
Second Brother is right.

244
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:58,679
What if this brat is hiding

245
00:10:58,759 --> 00:11:00,360
some of our manor's valuables on him?

246
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,519
Hurry up.

247
00:11:01,639 --> 00:11:03,039
Take off your clothes, piece by piece,

248
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:04,480
so we can inspect you properly.

249
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:11,440
Minister Ning,

250
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,840
what is your view on this?

251
00:11:14,639 --> 00:11:15,639
The Master has said

252
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,320
all matters of the manor are mine to manage.

253
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:20,399
As Matriarch of Ning Manor, I tell you:

254
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:21,960
You may leave,

255
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,519
but only after stripping bare.

256
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,639
Mother is right.

257
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:34,159
Once this bastard leaves Ning Manor,

258
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,039
taking his life afterward

259
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,799
will be effortless.

260
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:43,879
Lord Ning,

261
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,279
it seems being a kept man

262
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,639
isn't so easy after all.

263
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:53,559
Then open your pathetic eyes and watch closely.

264
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:05,159
You...

265
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,159
Father!

266
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:11,960
You wretched...

267
00:12:12,639 --> 00:12:13,480
wretched boy!

268
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,200
I came into Ning Manor alone,

269
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,639
and now I leave with nothing but myself.

270
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:25,039
But I ask all of you to remember this:

271
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,639
What happened today,

272
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,320
I will repay a hundredfold.

